OL,5, Women on the minimum wage in Ghana have
OL,6, to spend one in every seven dollars    
OL,7, they earn on sanitary pads, research by
OL,8, the BBC has found.                     
OL,10,FThe BBC surveyed nine countries around 
OL,11,FAfrica to see how affordable period    
OL,12,Fproducts are. We compared the minimum  
OL,13,Fwage to the local cost of the cheapest 
OL,14,Fsanitary pads and found they were      
OL,15,Fbeyond the reach of many women.        
